node.text:
Death leaves a heartache no one can heal, love leaves a memory no one can steal..

It's been almost a month since i lost my child #lucifer .. It's been a very difficult time :/ My whole space was a mess since then . Finally i got this courage from his love i'm sure which i felt like a soft voice whispering in my ear during this meditation session i had earlier , like to stop grieving for what i can not bring back but to rejoice whatever time i had :) 
So it's a new start again , which started from cleaning up my tiny space :) 

wishing to bring back the page vibrant energy asap :) and I'm sorry for everyone i couldn't reply when they were in need . i hope you all are doing good now ..
sending infinite love and light to everyone:) 

love and blessings #awaken_healers
